{"tid":1572642,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"［傷私鳥］唔該用永久性傷殘為目標，集中於一手/一腳/手指","createTime":"2019-09-15T17:25:00.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-13T16:34:55.000Z","uid":309192,"like":17,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"d721ee1ce484f3d5c39891a42f6efc64c74c13d5","tid":1572642,"uid":309192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T17:25:00.000Z","msg":"首先要記住，對家所有人都係零留手，次次傷得都係自己友，佢地必須要付出代價<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n多數佢地仆街之後手足就會用拳打腳踢/拎遮打<br />\n或者單插，但其實都只係打到多肉既位，<br />\n就算打頭都好佢地都會縮埋一舊保護到個頭部，<br />\n最多都只係做到皮外傷<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n建議：學狗咁禁實佢地再搵一隻手/腳/手指作為目標（當然唔怕殘忍/忍唔住就可以插眼）<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n做法：拉直其中一隻手腳，反方向咁重擊三次手肘/波羅蓋位<br />\n基本上佢係肯定金撚過比人圍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n但最好其實係玩手指，一來脆弱二來廢左基本上工都唔使番<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n一諗起藍絲廢老因爲殘廢搵唔到錢成為家人既負累<br />\n慢慢佢d屋企人就會覺得當日藍絲廢老係自己攞黎衰<br />\n諗到就爽YY<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"751d9f598bc082cdb11060ad2bebb359b59eb7f6","tid":1572642,"uid":307203,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T17:25:55.000Z","msg":"push<br />\n[品葱轉載] [文宣戰術] 教你如何宣傳反共，緊貼現在熱門事件。<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/ebhFbS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/ebhFbS</a>"},{"pid":"9750e2eeb618b6007d9bf785bb0d410b5df6a7e6","tid":1572642,"uid":267937,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T17:27:41.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"09c4f0c4573b6fe9a4a2eba6fd3617deb13f935c","tid":1572642,"uid":309192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T17:30:10.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"5a338aecc0887ddf3a6c4171fe9332f2cb4b5962","tid":1572642,"uid":93141,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T17:31:04.000Z","msg":"915 - 進步，改善，突破<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1572164/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1572164/page/1</a>"},{"pid":"d5fba03851c2f51553d3e4f636523e3b4a3d2e8f","tid":1572642,"uid":58453,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T17:32:47.000Z","msg":"岩呀 再見到 先屈斷一隻手拍 廢其集中力 之後放題住切 <br />\n<br />\n最緊要大大力錫春袋<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2f02a59e341a5cf106fc0d80e2fa8a63826b00bc","tid":1572642,"uid":124292,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T17:33:19.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"954cb758fc088095c76380d030ccba4f07ddd333","tid":1572642,"uid":57911,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T17:34:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"45f53d736a4ae52d409a11c7143a299e75332a2e","tid":1572642,"uid":191667,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T17:36:25.000Z","msg":"有遮就通佢坑渠啦<br />\n包佢嚟緊幾日去廁所都勁爽"},{"pid":"202d956f15d43571bfe0041eeeeb20265bf2f2a4","tid":1572642,"uid":24924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T17:39:49.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"2ce22ec7ad0c0fc068520e0c2615a93953a09f2c","tid":1572642,"uid":83060,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T18:04:40.000Z","msg":"其實用力踩小腿就得<br />\